    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This orange-yellow, gelatinous oil sparkles with tiny, ultrathin silver shards.</p>\n<p>The oil can coat one slashing or piercing weapon or up to 5 pieces of slashing or piercing ammunition. <strong>Applying the oil takes 1 minute.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong>: For 1 hour, the coated item is magical and has a <strong>+3 bonus to attack and damage roll</strong>s.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: This item will apply a DAE effect to the <strong>token targeted</strong> before the item is used.&nbsp; Players need to manage the appropriate use (e.g. doesn't help bludgeoning weapons) and only 5 pieces of ammunition.</p>",
